[section#extern.types
    [:en] Types
    [:zh_CN] 类型
]

[para]
[:en] For each type [`T] from the C standard library, the types [`::T] and [`std::T]
are reserved to the implementation and, when declared, [`::T] shall be identical
to [`std::T].
[:zh_CN] 对于每个 C 标准程序库中的类型 [`T]，类型 [`::T] 和 [`std::T] 均被实现保留，
并且当声明了它们时，[`::T] 应当等同于 [`std::T]。
